### Month Balance API - Testes
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5150
@token = seu-token-jwt-aqui

### ============================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ============================================

### 1.1 Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@teste.com",
  "password": "Senha123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Senha123!"
}

### 1.2 Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@teste.com",
  "password": "Senha123!"
}

### 1.3 Verificar se email existe
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/check-email/teste@teste.com

### ============================================
### 2. RECEITAS GLOBAIS (Incomes)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Listar todas as receitas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 Criar receita manual
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Salário",
  "type": 0
}

### 2.3 Criar receita por hora
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Freelance",
  "type": 1
}

### 2.4 Buscar receita por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.5 Atualizar receita
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Salário CLT",
  "type": 0
}

### 2.6 Deletar receita
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 3. DESPESAS GLOBAIS (Expenses)
### ============================================

### 3.1 Listar todas as despesas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 Criar despesa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Aluguel"
}

### 3.3 Criar outra despesa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Conta de Luz"
}

### 3.4 Buscar despesa por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.5 Atualizar despesa
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Aluguel + Condomínio"
}

### 3.6 Deletar despesa
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 4. DADOS DO MÊS (MonthData)
### ============================================

### 4.1 Buscar ou criar mês (Janeiro 2026)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.2 Listar todos os meses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.3 Duplicar mês (Janeiro → Fevereiro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/duplicate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceYear": 2026,
  "sourceMonth": 1,
  "targetYear": 2026,
  "targetMonth": 2
}

### 4.4 Deletar mês
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 5. RECEITAS DO MÊS (MonthIncomes)
### ============================================

### 5.1 Listar receitas do mês
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.2 Adicionar receita manual ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incomeId": 1,
  "grossValue": 5000.00,
  "netValue": 4000.00,
  "hourlyRate": null,
  "hours": null,
  "minutes": null
}

### 5.3 Adicionar receita por hora ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incomeId": 2,
  "grossValue": null,
  "netValue": null,
  "hourlyRate": 50.00,
  "hours": 40,
  "minutes": 30
}

### 5.4 Atualizar valores da receita no mês
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "grossValue": 5500.00,
  "netValue": 4400.00,
  "hourlyRate": null,
  "hours": null,
  "minutes": null
}

### 5.5 Remover receita do mês
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 6. DESPESAS DO MÊS (MonthExpenses)
### ============================================

### 6.1 Listar despesas do mês
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.2 Adicionar despesa ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expenseId": 1,
  "value": 1500.00
}

### 6.3 Adicionar outra despesa ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expenseId": 2,
  "value": 200.00
}

### 6.4 Atualizar valor da despesa no mês
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 1600.00
}

### 6.5 Remover despesa do mês
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### FLUXO COMPLETO DE TESTE
### ============================================

### PASSO 1: Registrar
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@teste.com",
  "password": "Senha123!",
  "confirmPassword": "Senha123!"
}

### PASSO 2: Login (copiar o token da resposta)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "usuario@teste.com",
  "password": "Senha123!"
}

### PASSO 3: Criar receita global
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Salário",
  "type": 0
}

### PASSO 4: Criar despesa global
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Aluguel"
}

### PASSO 5: Buscar mês (cria automaticamente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PASSO 6: Adicionar receita ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incomeId": 1,
  "grossValue": 5000.00,
  "netValue": 4000.00,
  "hourlyRate": null,
  "hours": null,
  "minutes": null
}

### PASSO 7: Adicionar despesa ao mês
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expenseId": 1,
  "value": 1500.00
}

### PASSO 8: Ver dados completos do mês (com saldo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/months/2026/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
